^V.label: Bus
^V.definition: A metallic strip or bar (typically copper, brass or aluminium) that conducts electricity. Or bus bar.

^z.label: Current
definition: Alternating Current - usually used for power measurements

^3.label: DC
^3.definition: Direct Current - usually used for digital control

^Bh.label: Estimation
^Bh.definition: For a (maybe virtual) point where values are not measured but estimated.
